  "instructions": [
    "Whisk olive oil, pineapple juice, lemon juice, oregano, paprika, salt, and pepper to make a marinade.",
    "Add sliced chicken to the bowl and coat it evenly; cover and refrigerate for 30 minutes.",
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "Grill chicken strips for 3-4 minutes per side until cooked through and slightly charred.",
    "While chicken cooks, warm flatbreads on the grill for 1-2 minutes per side until pliable.",
    "Cut grilled chicken into bite sized pieces and distribute them over the warmed flatbreads.",
    "Drizzle a little extra pineapple juice over the chicken for brightness.",
    "Sprinkle chopped parsley on top and serve immediately."
  ],
